# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/2.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.5.0] - 2026-06-19

### Added

- Added `OrderNotValid` exception.

## [0.4.0] - 2026-06-19

### Added

- Added `OperatorNotValid` exception.

## [0.3.0] - 2026-06-19

### Added

- Added `EntityRegistry` to entity module.

## [0.2.0] - 2026-06-19

### Added

- Added Formatters module.

## [0.1.0] - 2026-06-17

### Added

- Added Criteria module.
- Added DAO module.
- Added DomainEvent module.
- Added Entity module.
- Added Logger module.
- Added Model module.
- Added UnitOfWork module.
- Added ValueObjects module.

